widely used since the 1990s.  Compare  James ."]}]},{"name":"of","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["Short form of   Oswald   or any of the various other names beginning with <i>Os-</i>."],"variants":[]},{"name":"Westmorland","type":"LAST","attribution":"Dictionary of American Family Names © Patrick Hanks 2003, 2006.","meanings":["English (northern): variant of   Westmoreland  ."],"variants":[{"name":"Westmoreland","meanings":["English (Yorkshire and Lincolnshire): habitational name from the former region or county of Westmorland. The placename is recorded as <i>Westmoringa land</i><i>c.</i> 1150 and means ‘the land of the people living west of the moors’ (i.e. the Pennines), from Old English <i>west</i> ‘west, western’ + <i>mōr</i> ‘moor’ + the groupname suffix <i>-ingas</i> (genitive <i>-inga-</i>) + <i>land</i> ‘land’."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Copsi of Westmorland was born in 1150, in Westmorland, England, United Kingdom. He had at least 1 son and 1 daughter."},"et":{"1150–":"1150–Surnud","1170–1195":"1170–1195","1175–Female":"1175–Surnud","1150–Male":"1150–Surnud","1175":"1175","1195":"1195","1150":"1150","1170":"1170","Westmorland, England":"Westmorland, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1150–":"1150–Kuollut","1170–1195":"1170–1195","1175–Female":"1175–Kuollut","1150–Male":"1150–Kuollut","1175":"1175","1195":"1195","1150":"1150","1170":"1170","Westmorland, England":"Westmorland, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1150–":"1150–Décédé","1170–1195":"1170–1195","1175–Female":"1175–Décédée","1150–Male":"1150–Décédé","1175":"1175","1195":"1195","1150":"1150","1170":"1170","Westmorland, England":"Westmorland, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Copsi of Westmorland est né en 1150, à Westmorland, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Il a eu au moins 1 fils et 1 fille."},"de":{"1150–":"1150–Verstorben","1170–1195":"1170–1195","1175–Female":"1175–Verstorben","1150–Male":"1150–Verstorben",